---
description: Frontend standards
globs:
  - "frontend/**/*.ts"
  - "frontend/**/*.tsx"
---

For frontend code:
- Use TypeScript.
- Keep components small and reusable.
- Prefer simple state management.
- Build responsive views for analyst workflows.
- Fetch data cleanly from backend APIs.
- Favor clarity and interpretability over flashy styling.
- Use charts to support analysis, not decoration.
- Keep page layouts professional and easy to demo.